      <Value><![CDATA[<p>This programme is delivered by International Skill Development Corporation, with quality assurance from QMU. This means that ISDC’s faculty provide the teaching and student support, but QMU checks the standards of marking to make sure it is in line with UK higher education expectations.</p>
<p>The MBA programmes offered by ISDC aim to ensure knowledge, skills and innovation to develop and grow a new or existing business. Successful completion of the programme allows students to appreciate their knowledge while engaging in practical skills by enhancing essential competencies as decision-making, team work, leadership skills, business potential, negotiation skills, communication and presentation skills to develop unique business leaders.</p>
<p>It further aims to cover knowledge in a full range of business process, skills delivery in marketing, finance, business analytics, research and operations, human resources, strategy, business innovation to ensure that any student is able to master business administration skills required to succeed globally.</p>]]></Value>
